<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2612598>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Morphological characters of Moira atropos (MZUSP00280). (A) Aboral view; (B) Oral view; (C) Lateral view; (D) Aboral view of naked test; (E) Oral view of naked test; (F) Lateral view of naked test; (G) Posterior view; (H–J) Illustrations of pedicellariae of M. atropos provided by Chesher (1963); (H) Valve of pedicellaria from floor of ambulacrum; (I–J) Valves of pedicellariae from aboral region. ab: aboral surface; or: oral surface." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2612598/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

